1) to register user
parameter required name,email,password,image(file), type, mobile.
http://localhost:3000/api/register

2)To login User.
Require email and password.
http://localhost:3000/api/login

3)Update password
require User Id and updated password as an input parameter , requires user to be authenticated.
http://localhost:3000/api/update-password

4) Forgot password
require email of user. User dont need to authenticated to use this api
http://localhost:3000/api/forget-password

5)reset password
Require updated password.
http://localhost:3000/api/reset-password?token=NjbipU6EjfAUZsiJOcWUeYVvJMPEkovW 